description: Whip up a delicious spiced beef tortilla wrap with creamy avocado and crunchy Mexican-style salad. Try this easy recipe for a tasty dinner in a hurry.
keywords: Easy Beef & Mexican-Style Salad Tortilla Pockets
name: Easy Beef & MexicanStyle Salad Tortilla Pockets Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 375 g Old El Paso tortilla pockets kit

recipeInstructions.text: Fill pockets with beef, avocado, half the salad and a small dollop of salsa (from kit). Serve with remaining salad and remaining salsa.
